  "notes": "Andrew 'Pop' Gemeny. Born in St. Michaels, MD. Married Myrtelle M. Gordon on May 18, 1929 at an Episcopal Church in New York. One son: William Gordon Gemeny. After Myrtelle's death in 1967, married Lucy Belle Pittman on October 2, 1967 in Culpeper, VA. Recorded oral histories from 1974-1980, digitized by Steven Gemeny in 2007-2008. Lived at Gemeny Farm in Prince George's County. Siblings: Esther L. (1894-1967), Edgar Denny (1899-1988), Eva (1903-1974), Ferguson (1909-2009), Ruth (1910-1910). Died March 30, 1989 at age 92. Buried in Suitland, MD."
}